extends layout

block content
  // Hero Section with Group Photo
  section(class="relative bg-gray-50 py-16")
    div(class="container mx-auto px-6")
      div(class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12")
        h1(class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6") About The Entrepreneurship Club
        p(class="text-2xl text-gray-600") Fostering Innovation and Entrepreneurial Spirit at Ashoka University
    
    // Group Photo Section
    div(class="container mx-auto px-6")
      div(class="max-w-6xl mx-auto rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl")
        img(
          src="/images/about_us.jpeg"
          alt="E-Club Team Photo"
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
        )

  // Main Content Section
  section(class="py-16 bg-white")
    div(class="container mx-auto px-6")
      div(class="max-w-4xl mx-auto")
        // Introduction
        div(class="mb-12")
          h2(class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6") The Entrepreneurship Club (E-Club)
          p(class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4")
            | The Entrepreneurship Club (E-Club) at Ashoka University is a thriving student-led initiative dedicated to fostering entrepreneurial spirit, innovation, and business acumen on campus. Backed by the InfoEdge Centre for Entrepreneurship (CFE), the club serves as a platform for aspiring entrepreneurs to ideate, build, and scale their ventures while engaging with industry experts and thought leaders.
          p(class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
            | With a robust team of 80+ members, E-Club is structured across multiple verticals, each playing a pivotal role in shaping the entrepreneurial ecosystem at Ashoka.

        // Marketplace Initiative
        div(class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg")
          h3(class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4") About Ashoka Marketplace
          p(class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
            | The Ashoka Marketplace is an initiative of the Technology Vertical of The Entrepreneurship Club (E-Club) at Ashoka University. This platform serves as a bridge between student entrepreneurs and the campus community, providing a space for innovative products and services to thrive.

  // Stats Section
  section(class="py-16 bg-gray-50")
    div(class="container mx-auto px-6")
      div(class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto")
        div(class="text-center")
          h3(class="text-5xl font-bold text-custom-red mb-2") 80+
          p(class="text-xl text-gray-600") Active Members
        div(class="text-center")
          h3(class="text-5xl font-bold text-custom-red mb-2") 7
          p(class="text-xl text-gray-600") Vertical Teams
        div(class="text-center")
          h3(class="text-5xl font-bold text-custom-red mb-2") 100+
          p(class="text-xl text-gray-600") Successful Events

  // Call to Action
  section(class="py-16 bg-white")
    div(class="container mx-auto px-6")
      div(class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center")
        h2(class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6") Join Our Community
        p(class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8") Be part of the entrepreneurial revolution at Ashoka University
        a(
          href="/seller/register"
          class="bg-custom-red text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-xl font-semibold hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all duration-200 inline-block"
        ) Become a Seller